Product price is different on product listing page and product in the cart


Major

Windows 10 pro
Google Chrome

URL: https://qatest-dev.indvp.com/product/luxury-sparkle-crackers

Steps to reproduce:

1) Add product to cart
2) Open the mini cart on the top right corner (via header)
3) Compare the price

Expected result:
The product price in the cart is the same as on product listing page
	
Actual result:
Product price of a product is different on product listing page and on product in the cart

